      .content-inner
        h2 Desmond White
        h4.subtitle Editor-in-Chief
        p Desmond White is a high school teacher in Sugar Land, Texas, who writes when his students aren't looking. While he was the Writing Coordinator of HBU's Academic Success Center, he founded the student literary magazine 
          | 
          em Writ in Water. 
          | Rune Bear will be his second lit mag project, with its focus less on Literature with a capital L and more on the Weird and Wonderful. Des lives with his wife and two cats and the thousand howling strays she feeds by the cars. Des
          |
          a(href='https://desmondwrite.com/') blogs
          | , writes about 
          |
          a(href='(http://sequart.org/author/desmond-white/') comics
          | , and gives 
          |
          a(herf='https://badwritingadvice.com/') bad writing advice
          | . Find him on
          a(href='https://twitter.com/desmondwrite')  twitter!

    .container
      //- .image-container
        //- img.content-image(src='images/stuart.jpg' alt='Stuart Warren')
      .content-inner
        h2 Stuart Warren
        h4.subtitle Speculative Fiction Editor 
        p Stuart Warren writes fiction and magical realism and lives in a tiny apartment with books and a wife and baby. Occasionally he reads a book and writes about it on 
          |
          a(href='http://sequart.org/') Sequart.org
          | , but mostly he shouts from his 
          | 
          a(href='http://www.stuartjwarren.com/') blog 
          | about life and pop culture. Stuart is the author of 
          |
          a(herf='(https://www.amazon.com/Spirit-Orn-Novel-Stuart-Warren-ebook/dp/B00O2HBLZA/ref=asap_bc?ie=UTF8') Spirit of Orn 
          | and 
          a(href='https://www.amazon.com/Tall-Men-Other-Tales-Stories-ebook/dp/B079V7DCFY/ref=sr_1_fkmr0_2?ie=UTF8&qid=1522169500&sr=8-2-fkmr0&keywords=stuart+warren+spirit+of+on') Tall Men and Other Tales. 
          | He lives in Santa Barbara, California. Find him on
          |
          a(href='https://twitter.com/StuartJWarren')  twitter!
    .container
      //- .image-container
      //-   img.content-image(src='images/alyssa.jpg' alt='Alyssa Warren')
      .content-inner
        h2 Alyssa Warren
        h4.subtitle Supernatural Fiction Editor
        p Alyssa Warren is actually a hobbit in disguise. She enjoys the comforts of hearth and home, cooking and crocheting. When adventuring is impractical, she settles for burrowing into a good book or taking a walk beside the ocean with her husband and daughter. Good fun aside, Alyssa is the former marketing coordinator of Authentic Publishers and currently provides contracted editing and proofreading services for BroadStreet Publishing. Find her on
          |
          a(href='https://twitter.com/BooksTeaGeekery')  twitter!
    .container
      //- .image-container
      //-   img.content-image(src='images/brandon.jpg' alt='Brandon Patterson')
      .content-inner
        h2 Brandon Patterson
        h4.subtitle Web Developer
        p Brandon Patterson is the Web Developer of Rune Bear. He is also a full time Developer at Sabre Hospitality Solutions. He's passionate about new technology, computers, and music. When he's not coding he enjoys playing video games and strumming his guitar. He currently resides in Roanoke, TX with his fianc√©e and cuddly cat Lexie Grey. Find him on
          |
          a(href='https://twitter.com/brandnpatterson')  twitter!







